
Parameters are nothing but 
Key=value
In Jenkins
	User defined variables
You define the variable name and variable value

	Jenkins provided environment variables

Jenkins define the variable name and variable value
Use them for dynamic inputs in your scripts

Parametrized build : When the job is build, we provide the value of parameter or variables

1.	Add Parameters in the job and build it


Take an existing job

We will parameterize the github repo URL in the job

We will create parameter in the job

String parameter
 Description
 Default value

You will use the parameter in Jenkins script/pipelinecode or in any field of freestyle job

Refer to the parameter

For example:
Name of parameter is : username

Refer to it in script as :   ${username}

